data.title: Karya Khalil Gibran
data.meta_description: Karya Khalil Gibran.docx - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document lists the titles of 26 published works by Kahlil Gibran, an early 20th century Lebanese-American writer and artist. The works span Gibran's career from 1918 to 1995 and include his most famous work The Prophet published in 1923, as well as collections of poems, drawings, and philosophical essays.
